OL,7,FThe wife of a British man who was
OL,8,Fkilled whilst fighting for Ukraine
OL,9,Fdespite having no military experience
OL,10,Fsays her life is now in limbo.
OL,12,FAlan Williams, 35, from Wirral, has
OL,13,Fofficially been declared as Missing In
OL,14,FAction because his body has yet to be
OL,15,Fretrieved.
OL,17,FHis wife Stephanie says she had
OL,18,Fpleaded with him not to go but Alan
OL,19,Fwho had two children and two step-
OL,20,Fchildren was determined to help the
OL,21,FUkrainian people.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
