OL,7,FStephanie says Alan had suffered with
OL,8,Fhis mental health for a long time and
OL,9,Fearlier this year was hospitalised
OL,10,Fafter attempting to take his own life.
OL,12,FShe said: "We later found out that the
OL,13,Fday after he got discharged, he
OL,14,Fapplied for the Ukraine Foreign
OL,15,FLegion, which we didn't know about
OL,16,Fstraightaway.
