OL,3,CWife of British man killed whilst
OL,4,Cfighting in Ukraine tells of her
OL,5,Cheartache
OL,7,F"I told our GP and mental health team
OL,8,Fwhat he'd planned to do in the hope
OL,9,Fthat they'd see it as well this guy's
OL,10,Ftried to kill himself, he now wants to
OL,11,Fgo to a war zone, suicide by war but
OL,12,Fhe said that the structure would do
OL,13,Fhim good.
OL,15,F"We were gobsmacked that it was even
OL,16,Fsomething he was thinking about,
OL,17,Fscared, worried, we spent the four
OL,18,Fmonths trying to talk him out of it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
