OL,7,FStephanie says Alan had hidden his
OL,8,Fpassport because he knew she would
OL,9,Fconfiscate it to stop him flying out
OL,10,Fthere.
OL,12,FAlan flew out to Ukraine on May 7
OL,13,Fwhere he underwent training. The last
OL,14,Ftime Stephanie spoke to him was on
OL,15,FJuly 2 when his tone suddenly changed,
OL,16,Fafter he told her he was embarking on
OL,17,Fhis first mission.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
