OL,3,CWife of British man killed whilst
OL,4,Cfighting in Ukraine tells of her
OL,5,Cheartache
OL,7,F"I could tell by the way he was
OL,8,Ftalking to me it was a dangerous
OL,9,Fmission," she revealed. "I noticed the
OL,10,Fdifference in his tone and behaviour
OL,11,Fand it heightened my senses and I
OL,12,Fwould literally wake up at five in the
OL,13,Fmorning, check my phone, I would check
OL,14,Fit every hour, checking if he was
OL,15,Fonline.
OL,17,FOn July 15 Stephanie got a call from a
OL,18,FUkrainian Sergeant to say Alan was
OL,19,Fmissing in action, presumed dead.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@IO]qD@YOU
