OL,3,CWife of British man killed whilst
OL,4,Cfighting in Ukraine tells of her
OL,5,Cheartache
OL,7,F"His team got ambushed by four drones,
OL,8,Fone of them dropped a mortar eight
OL,9,Fmetres away from where they were."
OL,11,F"I've been told that Alan had his back
OL,12,Fto it when it dropped and was
OL,13,Funresponsive immediately. Obviously
OL,14,Fthey tried to go back for him, just
OL,15,Fcheck was OK, but mortars kept getting
OL,16,Fdropped on them.
OL,18,F"So the lads that were there with him
OL,19,Fhad to retreat because I know one was
OL,20,Finjured and I'm not sure about the
OL,21,Fother two.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
