OL,3,CWife of British man killed whilst
OL,4,Cfighting in Ukraine tells of her
OL,5,Cheartache
OL,7,F"They had to retreat, they kept
OL,8,Fcalling him calling his call sign out
OL,9,Fand a friendly drone operator said,
OL,10,Fhe's gone."
OL,12,FStephanie has been told it may be too
OL,13,Fdangerous for Alan's body to be
OL,14,Frecovered and is now in limbo.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
