OL,3,CWife of British man killed whilst
OL,4,Cfighting in Ukraine tells of her
OL,5,Cheartache
OL,7,F"It still doesn't feel real because
OL,8,Fwe've got no closure even though we
OL,9,Fknow by what we've been told that the
OL,10,Flikelihood is that he's dead and that
OL,11,Fit would be a miracle if he's just
OL,12,Fwounded somewhere, you still have that
OL,13,Ftiny bit of hope because we don't have
OL,14,Fthe proof."
OL,16,FStephanie's Mum has now started
OL,17,Ffundraising to help support Stephanie
OL,18,Fas without the proof that Alan is dead
OL,19,Fshe is unable to access financial help.
